name: 2nd International Conference on Biomedical Engineering
content: Biomedical Engineering 2020! We courteously invite you to be an Organizing Committee Member and Plenary speaker at our upcoming 2nd International Conference on Biomedical Engineering which will be held at Osaka, Japan during October 19-20, 2020\. This year we have adopted the theme “Latest Innovations & Researches in Biomedical Engineering”. Conference tracks will include research, Evaluation, New trends & technologies in Biomedical Engineering. We hope that you will be Strength to the Conference. For more information about the conference, PS: https://www.medwideconferences.com/biomedicalengineering/ We request you to kindly avail this opportunity to share your scientific excellences and be a part of the esteemed conference as soon as possible. Abstract Submission Link: https://www.medwideconferences.com/biomedicalengineering/submitabstract Hope you will Honor us by accepting our invitation. Reach back to us for further assistance. Thanks & Regards Rachel Martin Program Manager
